{"tid":181161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"安慰人有乜技巧？","createTime":"2017-03-31T12:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T04:24:52.000Z","uid":98645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f375ea3aecce772ea4691b57583b410ecc6e6e3","tid":181161,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"雖然自己唔係好掂，但平日身邊好多朋友都有好多煩惱，我成日鳩吓鳩吓，鍾意比advice，唔識點安慰人，好在我叫做口密，可以聽吓佢地講。<br />\n但最近發現有朋友有抑鬱，具體唔適合講，重點係好想自己可以做得好啲幫吓佢，唔想佢覺得無人理或者無人可以信之類。<br />\n有無啲咩係適合講，又或者調番轉係一定唔可以講？我聽佢講就話唔想人同佢加油，覺得好攰&hellip;各位有無咩建議比我？"},{"pid":"d04d6821a8db3b6dab6633432fabaa62aff54a40","tid":181161,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:01:20.000Z","msg":"想氹吓佢或者陪吓佢，但驚自己越搞越衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4f9150b5fd6b2c53da994724e3e82089068d34","tid":181161,"uid":52703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"你冇病下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47f287589f23bd9cda429b6df31c14271a55d4c","tid":181161,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想氹吓佢或者陪吓佢，但驚自己越搞越衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你就咪搞啦<br />\n冇果個能力點解又要多事"},{"pid":"fed074e1042b588fede3d649979a238c1758c65b","tid":181161,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:02:57.000Z","msg":"Do not TALK about too much, the key thing all you have to do is being a good LISTRNER"},{"pid":"5ef8fd07071431015376e7a1b7cf7ceb8ea8990e","tid":181161,"uid":61903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇過一本日本書<br />\n如果人地唔開心 千奇唔好叫佢 &ldquo;唔好唔開心啦&rdquo;<br />\n應該表示理解 之後果啲唔記得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢純粹呻都唔知點回應佢好"},{"pid":"d85d2a64548e18fb357ea25f5c67d14e15eec90d","tid":181161,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想氹吓佢或者陪吓佢，但驚自己越搞越衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你就咪搞啦<br />\n冇果個能力點解又要多事</blockquote><br />\n咁梗係唔係話想醫或者解決，但咁唔理佢係會好啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7900fd09f6840783967d78d31b7d29b145cff9","tid":181161,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Do not TALK about too much, the key thing all you have to do is being a good LISTRNER</blockquote><br />\n唔講唔提起 好似正常相處當無野咁 我又驚佢會以為我唔想理 但如果你無端端問佢會好odd 或者特登同佢講 話我肯聽咁？有無話點樣為之適合嘅listener嘅距離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b3c62157dd7724b06cd932d80abf2d14d28946","tid":181161,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前睇過一本日本書<br />\n如果人地唔開心 千奇唔好叫佢 &ldquo;唔好唔開心啦&rdquo;<br />\n應該表示理解 之後果啲唔記得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢純粹呻都唔知點回應佢好</blockquote><br />\n同埋表示理解會唔會都令佢反感 始終人人經歷或者感受唔同 即係類似之前喺youtube睇到vsauce啲科學片 話每個人睇到嘅紅色都唔同 無可能真係明佢經歷乜 所以又唔想咁輕易表示理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0885a927a2bdd70cc8a6767626004c0865718d","tid":181161,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"想話幫到人係咪將自己睇得太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b196da07888579f5f6dfbec32ba753247fd4fd20","tid":181161,"uid":83575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"俾佢知道你會係身邊陪住佢就得"},{"pid":"fd67bc99a15808c4c8cf183174b4aa6fd9f56b01","tid":181161,"uid":98645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re